Ranger Help for: ran
====================

SYNTAX:      ran <message>
             eran <message>
USAGE:       Anywhere

SUMMARY:
This command sends a message on the Ranger guild chat channel. All
online Rangers will see the message. Use 'ran' for standard messages
and 'eran' for emote-style messages. Guild chat is an out-of-character
communication channel for Rangers to coordinate, ask questions, and
socialize. Use 'ranhist' or 'rhist' to view recent chat history.
